data.title: Mark Dempsey
data.meta_description: Mark Dempsey. Actor: Im Paradies ist der Teufel los. Mark Dempsey was born on 29 January 1936 in West Hollywood, California, USA. He was an actor, known for Im Paradies ist der Teufel los (1963), Raumschiff Enterprise (1966) and Valley of the Dragons (1961). He died on 5 April 1994 in Seattle, Washington, USA.
